---
const chips = [
  'Cavite, Philippines',
  'TUP–Cavite · Computer Engineering',
  'Open to remote roles',
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-14 md:py-20 scroll-mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="animate-on-scroll">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">About</p>
      <div class="w-10 h-px bg-accent mb-12"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-5">
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-text-primary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm an aspiring AI/ML Engineer who ships production systems, not just experiments. My work spans
        agentic LLM pipelines, RAG architectures, and multimodal document AI — all deployed with
        live demos on Hugging Face Spaces.
      </p>
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
        I came up through fullstack web engineering — Django, MySQL, REST APIs at production scale
        (1000+ users on my thesis project) — and have spent the last year going deep on applied
        AI/ML, building systems that move beyond notebooks to real-world deployments.
      </p>
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
        Currently focused on:
        <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">agentic LLM systems</span>,
        <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">RAG architecture</span>, and
        <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">multimodal document AI</span>.
      </p>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll pt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {chips.map((chip) => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface border border-border text-text-muted text-xs font-mono rounded-sm">
            {chip}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
